Traction is ready to be translated to your language. Please follow these simple instructions:

1. Download the latest language pack from http://github.com/jestro/traction_languages (click the download button at the top).
2. Unzip the package and find the .po and .mo files for your language.
3. Create a /languages directory within your Traction theme directory or your Traction child theme directory and copy the .po and .mo files into that directory.
4. Define your language in your wp-config.php file.

Please help with translating Traction!

We have provided the traction.po and traction.mo files as a starting point for translating Traction into your language. If you have a completed translation and would like us to include it in the language pack please send your .po and .mo files to info {at} thethemefoundry.com.